title: 'Russia is Defending Europe by Fighting Terrorists in the Middle East'
text: Russia is the only nation helping European countries to deal with the refugee crisis by going against those who caused it, namely the Islamic State and other extremist groups in Syria, Mateusz Piskorski, who heads the European Center for Geopolitical Analysis, told Sputnik. ...
